<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN""http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>button-1</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/button-1.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="./../css/reset.css">

    <body>
        <h1>没有图标:定宽定高文字居中(一样大小),可扩展,统一背景(单div)</h1>
        <div class="onediv">
            &gt
        </div>
        <div class="button">
            <span class="icon">&gt</span>
        </div>
        <a class="button">
            <span class="icon">我是按钮</span>
        </a>
        <h1>只有图标,没有文字</h1>
        <a class="button">
            <span class="img"></span>
        </a>
        <h1>没有图标:左右间距固定,文字自动撑开,可扩展背景</h1>
        <div class="center">
            <div class="button2">
                <span class="txt">4545454564564464</span>
                <span class="txt">右边54545454444545454545454545fdsa</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <a class="center">
            <div class="button2">
                <span class="txt">左边</span>
                <span class="txt">右边</span>
            </div>
        </a>
        <h1>有图标,图标在左:左边定宽,右边文字撑开</h1>
        <div class="center">
            <div class="button3 left">
                <span class="icon"></span>
                <span class="txt">sdasdasdsadsasda</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="center">
            <div class="button3 right">
                <span class="icon"></span>
                <span class="txt">sdasdasdsadsasda</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <h1>图标在X,带竖杠</h1>
        <div class="center">
            <div class="button3 left">
                <span class="icon"></span>
                <span class="shugang"></span>
                <span class="txt">sdasdasdsadsasda</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="center">
            <div class="button3 right">
                <span class="icon"></span>
                <span class="shugang right"></span>
                <span class="txt">349128943</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="center">
            <div class="button3">
                <span class="icon icon_left"></span>
                <span class="shugang"></span>
                <span class="txt txt_center">sdasdasdsadsasda</span>
                <span class="shugang right"></span>
                <span class="icon icon_right"></span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="speech-bubble">Hi there!</div>
        <div class="center">
            <form>
                <input type="text" value="123">
                <input type="submit" class="test" value="submit2">
                <button type="submit" class="test">submit1</button>
            </form>
        </div>
        <iframe src="../button-2/index.html" width="20%" height="50%" id="iframe1">
            脚本之家使用了框架技术，但是您的浏览器不支持框架，请升级您的浏览器以便正常访问脚本之家。
        </iframe>
    </body>
</head>

</html>
